s 2032 -192 100 0 Gemini Telescope Control System
s -544 240 100 0 Note that the output links will send data to the input
s -544 208 100 0 fields of the subsystem CAD even if the command is
s -544 176 100 0 rejected by the TCS. The data sent will be the same
s -544 144 100 0 as in the last valid command. This is fairly
s -544 112 100 0 innocuous but will leave the subsystem CAD marked. If
s -544 80 100 0 this might cause a problem then a custom schematic should
s -544 48 100 0 be cloned from this one where the outputs are only sent 
s -544 16 100 0 when the STLK link is triggered.
